SEGAL--Howard, on February 27, 2014 at 71 years of age. Beloved husband of Ronnee. Loving father of Jeffrey Segal and Stephanie Hartman (Brian). Stepfather of Julie Gerstenblatt (Brett) and Greg Medow (Ursula). Brother of Elinor Hirsch (Robert) and the late Norman Segal (Gail Clott). Adoring grandfather of Ethan, Jaime, Andrew, Zoe, Boden and Knox. Cherished friend of Phyllis Segal. He was an honorable attorney and a proud graduate of Lehigh University. He touched many lives and will be missed by all. Services Sunday, 9:30am at Central Synagogue, 55 St. and Lexington Ave.